hopobject.body: Other amount hollywood diet drops deutsch Our hero is Cormoran Strike, an ex-soldier who lost a leg in Afghanistan and is now a hard-drinking private investigator with a complicated private life. His secretary Robin is a spirited woman who joins him from a temp agency. Cue some low-key sexual tension between them. Strike investigates various disreputable friends – including a nasty fashion designer and a rapper named Deeby Macc – to build up a picture of the dead girl.
